  "title": "True Horror Template",
  "description": "True First person view Horror template.",
  "longDescription": "<p>Special discount offer (old price 49$)</p><p><br /></p><p>This project will allow you to create your own horror game easily. The template has its own <u>Main menu</u> with a configure <u>option tab</u> as well as a <u>credits tab</u>. The player has several widgets: a central point to <u>interact</u>, a <u>gameover menu</u> when he dies, a widget for the <u>objectives</u>, for the <u>pause menu</u> as well.</p><p><br /></p><p>This project use third person character body player from third person template.</p><p><br /></p><p>To embellish the game user interface, an <u>animated heartbeat widget</u> is coupled to the sprint to simulate the heartbeat speed due to the sprint, finally the <u>camera mode</u> which is in my opinion the most important thing of the project, has the ability to<u> zoom forwards and backwards,</u> to be able to <u>pick up</u> its <u>batteries</u> to be able to recharge the camera but also a <u>night vision</u> mode. The camera has its <u>own time rec</u> in <u>real time</u> for more realism and have full sound effect included.</p><p><br /></p><p>The player can <u>hide into a locker</u> and can be <u>chased by the AI</u>. To avoid being <u>caught</u>, the player can use the <u>camera security system</u> to look around the map.<u> </u></p><p><u>Doors</u> can be locked and opened by simple <u>key</u>.</p><p>The player can also <u>unlock doors</u> using <u>keypad</u> , by finding a predetermined <u>4-digit combination</u> of your choice.</p><p>The project also contains <u>10 custom sounds</u> ranging from camera sounds to Main Menu ambient or effect sounds that blend perfectly with visual effects such as hallucinations or blurred vision.</p><p><br /></p><p>38 high definition scans of unique paintings created by my own hands. Each piece was made with acrylic paint, the quality of the scans will allow you to resize the pictures to be used in your own levels according to your wishes. (canvas frame included)</p><p><br /></p><p>The template has a fully customizable menu, with its option menu with the possibility of saving its settings. As well as the possibility of automatically choosing the best settings by clicking on the optimized button. the menu also has a credits tab and can play sequences in real time</p><p>VIDEO:</p><p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/jpC6L8AH7G8\" rel=\"nofollow\">Painting Showcase</a>, <a href=\"https://youtu.be/3cSF4XkSxJo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Showcase 2</a>, <a href=\"https://youtu.be/azoYHvTd5qw\" rel=\"nofollow\">Folder Showcase</a></p><p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/NWDnjkUbh5A\" rel=\"nofollow\">HeartBeat Widget</a></p><p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/IlRhkYgmlLw\" rel=\"nofollow\">MAIN MENU</a></p><p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/RrITu04UB7g\" rel=\"nofollow\">GAMEPLAY VIDEO</a></p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZSmyUCj98Ew\" rel=\"nofollow\">GAMEPLAY VIDEO</a> ( ENVIRONNEMENT not included)</p><p><br /></p><p>Input: ZQSD to move, E for action, R to Reload, O to show/hide objectives, H to hide in locker ,F for nightvision, P for pause ,SPACE to jump, Right Mouse button for camera mode ,Mouse wheel for zoom in/out ,left Mouse button for interact with keypad ,Left Shift for sprint</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>&#xfeff;</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>New ; <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/WWdUtqJB\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord</a> server for better support.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>If you have idea to mecanics you would like to see please leave a comment .</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>DOCUMENTATION <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Uhwe43Y2PyPn9z9L0c335d5oerUhQlpc/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>For any question contact me at : Chief2.0&#64;protonmail.ch</p>",
