  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>Character:life and damage,pause widget,heartbeat widget,sprint,camera mode,can be caught by AI,line trace, camera battery pickup and reload system, can hide in locker and more.</li><li>Full Main menu with option and credits. Using real time feature or/and sequence video.</li><li>Interactable Keypad using 4 digit combination. Can be combined with what your need easily.</li><li>Camera Switcher: Allow to use external camera for playing between first person camera and third person camera like in old classic game and switch between view .</li><li>Smart AI: patrolling, chasing, roaming, catch player. The Ai can patrolling in the area where the last player location is know, the AI can also kill the player in locker if the AI seeing the player while hiding .Ai have own blackboard and logic and can be fully customized. when catch an smooth animation is played as finisher before show the game over screen &#43; gameover screen</li><li> Locker:The locker can be used to hide the player, using a smooth transition the locker can be used with third person character.</li><li>Security computer and security camera:allow quickly the player to access a computer and look over each area you want. You can also use multiple security computer with own security camera.Each camera move automatically.</li><li>Door and key: Simple door blueprint can be locked and opened with a key.Key can be pickup by player.</li><li>Flickering Light easy customable&#43;Post process effect Blur and hallucination &#43;Custom Font and Custom sound.</li><li> Full camera system.</li></ul><p>28 BPs,2 levels,12 widget bp ,1 behavior tree,1 blackboard,2 fonts,10 sounds ,1 sequence,53 mat,53 tex,9 SM.</p><p>Windows: Yes</p><p><br /></p>",
